<section class="cta">
  <h2>O futuro do seu dinheiro começa aqui.</h2>
  <p>Junte-se a milhares de usuários que já escolheram a liberdade.</p>
  <a href="/checkout" class="btn btn-primary btn-cta">Começar Agora</a>
</section>

</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    padding: 8rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Optional background effect/glow behind CTA */
  .cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    filter: blur(40px);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #ff0080);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.2);
  }

  .cta p {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .btn-cta {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    padding: 1.2rem 3rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.4);
  }

  .btn-cta:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.6);
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.05);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cta {
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .cta h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .cta p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .btn-cta {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
